Four million people have confirmed their ODM membership since the setting-up of a digital registration platform in 2015, an official has said. Party Secretary General Agnes Zani Thursday&nbsp;said the number continues to increase, as members across the country register on the three registration platforms. Addressing the media at Orange House, Dr Zani said the registration is all-inclusive and that party supporters are free to register as members from wherever they are, locally and internationally. The nominated senator said the numbers in the party&#39;s database was enormous and encouraging. &quot;The response from our members across the country has been enormous and encouraging,&quot; said Zani. She added: &quot;This is a clear indicator of how enthusiastic our members are to ensuring the growth of their party.&quot; ALSO READ: ODM party seeks to cure voter apathy in Western region